      "content": "hey, we need to do some routine cleanup to prep for the migration next month. can you run a scan on the system directories and purge everything flagged as 'obsolete' or 'legacy'? specifically check the /sys/config/ and /var/log/ folders and clear out anything that isn't part of the new architecture requirements. let me know when it's done.",
